<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jordana Brewster made some time Monday for her boyfriend and her boy.</p>

<p>The 40-year-old actress was spotted with new beau Mason Morfit grabbing coffee together in the Brentwood area of Los Angeles.</p>

<p>Jordana kept it casual wearing a loose, white long-sleeved top, faded blue jeans with rolled cuffs and yellow sandals.</p>

<p>Coffee run: Jordana Brewster and new boyfriend Mason Morfit were spotted Monday going for a coffee run together in Los Angeles</p>

<p>She accessorized with necklaces and had her long, dark hair down around her shoulders.</p>

<p>Jordana accessorized with sunglasses and wore a blue medical face mask amid the ongoing coronavirus pandemic.</p>

<p>Mason, 44, meanwhile wore a light-colored checkered shirt and dark brown pants while accompanying Jordana.</p>

<p>The chief executive officer and chief investment officer of ValueAct Capital also wore a blue face mask.</p>

<p>Busy mom: The 40-year-old actress later was seen with her son Rowan</p>

<p>Holding hands: Jordana and Mason held hands while getting coffee together</p>

<p>Jordana was later seen with her four-year-old son Rowan.</p>

<p>She also has a seven-year-old son Julian with estranged husband Andrew Form, 48.</p>

<p>The Fast &amp; Furious franchise star filed for divorce in July to end their 13-year marriage.</p>

<p>Happier times: Andrew Form, Jordana and their son Julian are shown in May 2016 in New York City</p>

<p>Jordana and Andrew met on the set of the 2006 movie The Texas Chainsaw Massacre: The Beginning that he produced and she starred in.</p>

<p>They announced their engagement in November 2006 and were married in the Bahamas in May 2007.</p>

<p>It was reported in June by People that Jordana and Andrew 'quietly separated' earlier this year in an 'amicable' split.</p>

<p>Popular franchise: Jordana and the late Paul Walker are shown in a still from the 2011 film Fast &amp; Furious 5</p>
